q1. How to disable web server in spring boot?
https://www.baeldung.com/spring-boot-no-web-server#:~:text=The%20easiest%20way%20to%20prevent,POM%20or%20Gradle%20build%20file

1. do not include in the dependency
2. use spring application builder
3. use application properties : spring.main.web-application-type=none

